<paragraph blockId="3.[136,1452,1824,2031]" pageId="3" pageNumber="72">
Diagnosis:—differing from the phylogenetically and morphologically closest related species 
<taxonomicName box="[1164,1284,1824,1850]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Tricholomataceae" genus="Bonomyces" kingdom="Fungi" order="Agaricales" pageId="3" pageNumber="72" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="arnoldii">
